If you don&#8217;t mind let&#8217;s just stick to the info I wanted to share with everyone in my initial post.<br />
When properly configured the brute force protection feature of the iThemes Security plugin is perfectly capable of dealing with this new amplification attack through xmlrpc.<br />
Impact on server load can be also be minimized.<br />
Try it and you will see,<br />
The info I&#8217;m sharing is based on actual test results &#8230;</p>
