		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>FYI We managed to get CloudFlare to add a special WAF rule for this to their WP rule list, you have to manually enable though. So that&#8217;s a quick fix for many people, if they can&#8217;t block XML-RPC entirely (CloudFlare also lets you do this).</p>
<p>From our own WAF rule tests, it appears that the official WordPress mobile apps use the system.multicall method. Which makes it that much harder to restrict 🙁</p>
		</div>

		
		
	</article>
